      "score": 243,
      "comments": 308,
      "author": "hershyb_",
      "published": "2026-07-16T20:03:23Z",
      "bullets": [
        "Comparing Claude Fable 5 and GPT-5.6 Sol reveals differences in multi-agent orchestration of generative video APIs under a strict $100 budget.",
        "Modern video pipelines leverage LLMs to generate prompts, manage temporal consistency, and synthesize audio-visual assets via Sora or Runway Gen-3.",
        "High-yield production at scale requires optimizing API rate limits, parallelizing asset generation, and automating video-audio alignment via orchestration frameworks."
      ]
    },
    {
      "source": "lobsters",
